17-12-08T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>防止民主派「DQ」建制派的立法會主席選舉參選人 <br />\n●日後不再由在立法會最資深的議員主持選舉，改為由立法會秘書主持選舉(廖長江第24條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申好似係最資深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走左去唔dq 大口狗，千古罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440ac195b3901525a4290a9e575033c73b7e823d","tid":491100,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79c8857aa47721fb6d21885205483d7caf08dcf9","tid":491100,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}